{"tid":2272629,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"襲警案警長口供與新聞片不符 辯方斥證供不盡不實","createTime":"2020-11-05T07:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T07:30:58.000Z","uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b69fd93c74e46914e7a4fe97719f6c4f52fa79da","tid":2272629,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:27:15.000Z","msg":"去年9月網民發起「和你飛2.0」，示威者堵塞機場及多區交通。當晚有設計師被指在將軍澳先後襲擊總督察及警署警長，．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．，批評警長作供「不盡不實」，又指兩名高級警務人員在記錄錄取口供的時間上，不約而同出現「疏漏」，辯方因而感到不安，認為兩警證供不可信。主任裁判官徐綺薇將案件押後至本月13日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n被告設計師李逸恒（24歲）被控於去年9月1日凌晨時分，在將軍澳常寧遊樂場用雨傘襲擊總督察丁家豪及警署警長林華平．．．．．．．．．．。其中林於今年6月曾在區院法官沈小民主審的一宗黃大仙暴動案中出庭作供。<br />\n<br />\n辯方早前盤問林時，引述<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">黃大仙暴動案判詞</span></span>，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">指林曾遭法官評為「不可靠證人」。</span></strong></span>林一度不忿，並指法庭沒有直接向他講述判詞。辯方今陳詞時直斥林的說法是「匪夷所思」，指林有出庭作供的經驗，其解釋明顯是「強詞奪理」、「信口雌黃」，進一步削弱林作為證人的可信性。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又指，．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．由於被告被捕時不斷掙扎，所以在同僚為被告上手銬前，林一直用手控制被告。惟辯方昨播放一段無綫新聞片段，顯示被告當時蹲在地上，惟上手銬前仍能用手脫掉口罩，而被告被捕時身後只得一名警員。林同意．．．．．．．．．．．，但無法解答他當時身處的位置。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又指，兩名警方證人在口供紙上記錄的時間，均與記事冊內容不脗合，「連總督察、警署警長都有咁嘅情況」，情況令人不安。．．．．．．．．．林僅稱：「唔想claim OT。」辯方形容說法「狡辯」，引述《警察通例》指所有警員必須在記事冊註明逾時執行的工作內容，「佢可以先記錄，然後再決定是否claim OT；唔會因為佢寫咗，就夾硬塞錢畀佢」。<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官徐．．．．將案件押後至本月．．．日裁決。"},{"pid":"6f8c4a82bd374e121893c86bce82280cf1fbf6fa","tid":2272629,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:27:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/WKTSC4VVJZFYHNFL4EIJRHXVMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FWKTSC4VVJZFYHNFL4EIJRHXVMQ%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4DY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=3daf4889\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FWKTSC4VVJZFYHNFL4EIJRHXVMQ%2F&h=589bd97d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/WKTSC4VVJZFYHNFL4EIJRHXVMQ/</a>"},{"pid":"80caa168c9f82d2a222c08dbe9a5e5e91c1d5372","tid":2272629,"uid":263200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:30:36.000Z","msg":"證供有出入，證明冇夾口供，係誠實證人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705188c1ae3120f56294a5977e37785d65d40ed5","tid":2272629,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:30:58.000Z","msg":"呢個林狗作口供都唔係第一次～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/10-1-%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99-20-%E6%AD%B2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E5%8F%97%E5%AF%A9-%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E5%85%A9%E5%BA%A6%E6%A3%8D%E6%AF%86%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA-%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%9B%BE%E6%89%93%E9%A0%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F10-1-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599-20-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AF%25A9-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%25A3%258D%25E6%25AF%2586%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%25A0%25AD%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4DY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=adf97ef8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F10-1-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599-20-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AF%25A9-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%25A3%258D%25E6%25AF%2586%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D